main event: UFO sighted from three aircraft over Iwojima on February 21, 1960.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 11 minutes,The UFO was observed at an approximate altitude of 7,000 ft.,It was reported as a probable meteor by the reporting officers,Three aircraft confirmed the sighting at different locations,The Japanese pilot initially thought the object was a missile.
sighted object: UFO possibly identified as a meteor
witness description: officers and pilots from military aircraft
